Congratulation Team Coke studio Pakistan!

Just listened the first songs of season 9 I would like to say that truly "Ye sab uska hi karam hai ki baat abhi tak bani hui", 
coke studio Pak once again brings the music which felt like it's blessed by God,  voice of Abida make you feel that energy.
Like every season you guys are again able to bring the freshness in your music which show the dedication and love you have for your music and work. 
Great job guys!

Wish you all a happy and successful life.

From Bluecity of Rajasthan, India
